Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:11.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寬恕促人前行 仇恨讓人停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:16.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:21.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒讓你一直停滯不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:26.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:36.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名為永不凋謝之花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:41.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也無法永不凋謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:46.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}認真活著就會有回報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:51.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此斷言的話語必定是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:56.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之幾十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:01:01.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之幾不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:11.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:16.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:21.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:27.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原諒你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:29.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.13,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:23.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くこの手で掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:36.32,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:42.99,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:49.62,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:56.59,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:02.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして？　いま　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が解らなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:09.35,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:16.11,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境無く燃える焔　 群衆が指をさす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.82,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと強くなって　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.74,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.12,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したいひとを想い　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:30.83,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}闇をこの手で払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.13,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這樣 追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:23.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要親手去緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:36.32,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 則無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:42.99,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強顏歡笑也一樣 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:49.62,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無法保護珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:56.59,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:02.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼？ 我會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無人知曉也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:09.35,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:16.11,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃盡萬物的烈焰 飽受非議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.82,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.74,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保護所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.12,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心懷所愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:30.83,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}親手驅散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.83,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得知明陀要加入正十字騎士團的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我覺得一切都會變好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是 那個人卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您不打算加入騎士團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 別打擾住持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別看我這樣 我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有很重要的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}疑竇一旦萌生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便無法輕易消除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如說 疑竇演變成了更深的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一點點侵蝕著我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像毒液逐漸流遍全身一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:32.04,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,556)\fad(150,0)}蛇與毒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是一個叫「明陀宗」的寺院裡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你和志摩學長很熟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩學長有女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想給他做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道他喜不喜歡吃煎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他喜歡什麼牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}收到什麼禮物會很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什麼牌子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們別問我了 去問他本人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡是你每天吃午飯的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你無法融入班級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看你在學校和驅魔塾都是獨來獨往的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我並不是說這樣不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不太喜歡人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想過要改變自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是勉強自己去變得和其他人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就難免產生副作用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而越是掙扎 想要適應脫離正軌的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受的傷就會越深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣不是十分痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一個優秀的驅魔師 不應該很擅長團隊合作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}合作精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有句話我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「一帆風順的寂寞」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}山頭火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:05:01.20,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：這是日本俳句家 種田山頭火的名句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這你都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人的一生或許就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要不要做一做我出的課題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說不定能從中找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這叫什麼課題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不就是幫他打雜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼這隻猴子會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才要說這話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然知道還會有另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但沒想到會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼休息日都要看到你這張白痴臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這也是我想說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我向藤堂老師借了本很想看的書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就說好了幫他做事作為謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後他昨天放學後就突然來找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你才是 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啦 事已至此 也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不然就更醜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總之我們別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是一直吵下去 還不知道什麼時候能回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等會給找到的囀石貼上符 放到包裡帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總之先都放在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去這邊找 你就在那邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎麼理所當然地開始指揮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在這邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你去那邊好找一點的地方找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳這女人真是一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我請你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不是特地買給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老師說還有一個人 我就多帶了一瓶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當然 我自己也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才不要你請客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是一丁點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你有朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你總是一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那又怎麼樣 關你什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有人拜託我照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜託你照顧我？ 難道是父親大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 是住持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她是個好孩子 只是很容易被人誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以你要好好照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然您這麼吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}達摩大人 您為什麼不加入正十字騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果您真的為明陀著想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的沒有忘記身為明陀座主的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道不該身先士卒 成為驅魔師來引導大家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而您卻遊手好閒 經常不知所蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:10:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最近甚至連為門徒講經都不認真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您在做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道明陀不重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣就差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}否則藤堂老師要擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的比你少多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等會再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日落後就是惡魔活躍的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別小看這些囀石 不然可是要吃苦頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好 快丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 婀蜜哩帝 吽 癹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}錫杖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別去碰那些看起來太強的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}差一點就被它砸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過 你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可沒拜託你來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多管閒事的猴子 真是自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都說沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我揹你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為 為什麼我要讓志摩家的猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逞強也給我適可而止一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣就不能把囀石帶回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等會沒那麼痛了我自己會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你自己先回去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是白痴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那不過是些囀石而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當然是人更要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是說你會為了把囀石帶回去 放著受傷的人不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次再來就是 想收集多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你太死腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快上來 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}七 八 九 十
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別跑 猴子們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准接近這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在這裡啊 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你爸爸很擔心你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮也變重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個時候 我絲毫沒有懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要跟著住持就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持一定能指引大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我如此堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼 為什麼變成了現在這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了 疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼住持不加入正十字騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為還有別的事要做吧 他之前不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別的事是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然身為明陀宗的座主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道不應該身先士卒 加入正十字騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}教誨並指引門徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不就是座主的職責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一直都是這麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是我第一次和別人說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持有住持的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們身為門徒 只要相信他就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}畢竟他是住持 我們只能相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你的腳這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我剛才帶她去醫務室了 是扭傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}囀石沒能帶回來 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天我會去帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生同學沒有大礙真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要和寶生同學討論一下課題的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩同學你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有什麼事就聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他和我認識的人很像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然性格和長相完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他不會迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}強大且優秀 忠實地履行著自己的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他一定會成為受人愛戴與尊敬的優秀驅魔師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}與他相比 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不需要去成為別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最重要的是時刻對現狀保持疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就能夠做到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是好利用的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要選誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然還是選你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人啊 越是想要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就越容易被束縛 被自己的猜疑心吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你有這樣的潛質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:18:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就請你好好為我所用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寶生蝮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這事你不要說出去 你知道不淨王的左眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}左眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還 還有這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實我一直都覺得梅菲斯特理事長的行動很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我懷疑你們的座主 勝呂達摩和他串通起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會 住持他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你願意協助我嗎 寶生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一切都是為了保護我深愛的明陀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們總有一天會理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這樣 我決定迎娶蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你自作主張什麼呢 我可什麼都沒答應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}答應？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天你不是自然地答應了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別 別在這種地方胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要殺了你 殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混蛋猴子 你對姐姐大人做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不會吧 柔哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你居然喜歡那種骨瘦如柴的蛇女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你應該找個性感豐滿的金髮美女結婚才行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說什麼 志摩家的色猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不許你侮辱姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰是色猴子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害 你哥哥要結婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}變成親戚了 真尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}戀愛這種東西是沒有道理可講的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出雲 你經驗這麼豐富嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造哥和蝮姐的寶寶會長什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吧 真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小寶寶一定會特別可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已經聊到孩子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別這樣 我想都不敢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼睛像柔造 鼻子像蝮之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我完全沒話說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後雙方的家長都欣然同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一般不會不同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮好像並不太願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是 姐姐大人怎麼可能嫁給你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是認真的 你真的不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是要受罰的 怎麼可能被允許結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就乾脆把和我結婚當做受罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這種play
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才不像你這麼傻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而 而且
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不覺得這算是懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我再次請求 蟒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請把蝮託付給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才是 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 我還沒同意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大團圓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家怎麼都這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我都無語了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣一來就是Happy End了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說是吧 勝呂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊 撒旦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 我怎麼直接成撒旦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別玩了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乾脆直接叫撒旦大人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣多好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
